# 16 - Fitness Program Designer
# Create personalized workout plans

NAME fitness-designer
INPUT fitness_goal
INPUT current_fitness DEFAULT "sedentary"
INPUT equipment DEFAULT "minimal home equipment"
INPUT days_per_week DEFAULT 4

GOAL assess "Understand the goal: $fitness_goal from $current_fitness level with $equipment, training $days_per_week days/week."
GOAL design "Design a progressive program: exercises, sets, reps, rest periods, and weekly progression."
GOAL schedule "Create a $days_per_week-day weekly schedule with muscle group splits and recovery days."
GOAL guide "Add form cues for key exercises, warm-up/cool-down routines, and nutrition tips. Save the complete program to fitness-program-output.md."

RUN create USING assess, design, schedule, guide
